metadata.description: The FIRST ELEVEN CLUB is a private collection of unique digital NFTs. The First Eleven Founding Six are stored as ERC-721 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain and hosted on IPFS. With more than 150+ hand drawn traits, each NFT is unique and comes with a membership to an exclusive group of successful investors. Join an ambitious ever-growing community with multiple benefits and utilities.
